              <colophon  xml:id="coloph1">
                <locus from="87v" to="88r"/>
                <date notBefore="1514" notAfter="1515" evidence="internal"/> 
                <note>The colophon states that the manuscript was written in <placeName ref="gn:281184">Jerusalem</placeName> in the <date calendar="grace">Year of Grace 167</date>
                  by <persName ref="PRS11118Tewogolos"/>, a monk of the <persName ref="PRS11232HouseSam"/>
                  while the superior was <persName ref="PRS11115FereKr"/> of the order
                  of <persName ref="PRS11208HouseTakla"/>, the <roleName type="title">maggābi</roleName> <persName ref="PRS11116GabraN"/> of the 
                  <persName ref="PRS11232HouseSam"/> and the <roleName type="title">qāyǝm</roleName>
                  <persName ref="PRS11117Samuel"/> of the order of <persName ref="PRS10445Yonaso"/>. 
                  See also <bibl><ptr target="bm:Uhlig1988Palaographie"/><citedRange unit="page">365-366</citedRange></bibl>.</note>
               
               በአኰቴተ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ተጽሕፈት፡ ዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ አመ፡ <date calendar="grace">፻፷ወ፯፡ ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት፡</date>
                <date type="evangelists">በመዋዕለ፡ ሉቃስ፡ ወንጌላዊ፡</date> አሜሃ፡ አበቅቴ፡ ፬፡
                  ወመጥቅዕ፡ ፳ወ፯፡ ወተፈጸመት፡ በ<placeName ref="gn:281184">ኢየሩሳሌም፡</placeName> ሀገረ፡ ሰላም። አመ፡ 
                <date>፳ወ፭፡ ለመስከረም፡ በዕለተ፡ ዐርብ፡ ጊዜ፡
                    <gap reason="ellipsis" extent="unknown" resp="PRS10747Zotenbe"/> ሰዓተ፡</date>
                መዓልት። በመዋዕለ፡ ራይስ፡ <persName ref="PRS11115FereKr">ፍሬ፡ ክርስቶስ፡</persName> ወልደ፡ አቡነ፡ 
                <persName ref="PRS11208HouseTakla">ተክለ፡ ሃይማኖት</persName>።  
                ወ<roleName type="title">መጋቢ፡</roleName> <persName ref="PRS11116GabraN">ገብረ፡ ኖላዊ፡</persName> ወልደ፡ 
                <persName ref="PRS11232HouseSam">አቡነ፡ ሳሙኤል፡ ዘገዳመ፡ ዋሊ።</persName> ወ<roleName type="title">ቃይም፡</roleName> 
                <persName ref="PRS11117Samuel">ሳሙኤል፡</persName> ወልደ፡ አቡነ፡ 
                <persName ref="PRS11332Houseof">ዮናስ</persName>። 
                ወጸሓፊሃኒ፡ ወልደ፡ አባ፡ <persName ref="PRS11232HouseSam">ሳሙኤል፡ ዘገዳመ፡ ዋሊ፡</persName> 
                <persName ref="PRS11118Tewogolos">ቴዎጎሎስ፡</persName> ኃጥእ፡ 
                ወአ<supplied reason="undefined" resp="PRS10747Zotenbe">ባ</supplied>ሲ። ወእለ፡ አንበብክሙ፡
              </colophon>
              
